name: MahaDAO
public_notice: MahaDAO (MAHA) has migrated from their older ETH contract to a new one. For more information, please view this announcement on Telegram.

description.en: The MahaDAO is a decentralised organisation that aims to revolutionizing money. MahaDAO is a community focused DeFi project empowering billions to create timeless value through the ARTH token, the world's first valuecoin.
